casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 434 U. S. 809.]

Report of the Special Master on Obligation of New Mexico to Texas under the Pecos River Compact received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, together with supporting briefs to the Report may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies, if any, with supporting briefs, to such exceptions may be filed within 30 days.
